						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vīrarājēndradēva. Year [4]: A.D. 1210.</hi></p>						

						<p>Gift of one <hi rend="italic">achchu</hi> for a twilight lamp <hi rend="italic">(chandhyā dīpam)</hi> to be lighted in the shrine of Periyanāchchiyār by Chiṅgaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Aṅgarāyaṉ, the son of Uttamachōḻap pallavaraiyan of Muttūr. Kācuvan Bhaṭṭan Uḍaiyan <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kuladīpa Bhaṭṭan, a <hi rend="italic">śiva-brāhmaṇa</hi> of the Periya Nāchchiyār temple and his descendants shall maintain the lamp. (see Nos. 158, 166).</p>						

